- `.\backend\repositories\BaseRepository.js`
  - Gaps: `church_id` is optional in core methods (security risk).
  - Remedy: Enforce `church_id` in constructor or core methods; implement mandatory pagination.
- `.\backend\repositories\UserRepository.js` / `.\backend\repositories\UsersRepository.js`
  - Gaps: Duplicated logic; manual role-update loops are not atomic.
  - Remedy: Consolidate; use a single transaction for user + role updates.
- `.\backend\repositories\ChurchRepository.js`
  - Gaps: Executes 4 sequential count queries for stats.
  - Remedy: Consolidate into a single aggregated scan or CTE.
- `.\backend\repositories\DepartmentsRepository.js`
  - Gaps: `getAllWithStats` has high N+1 risk (3 correlated subqueries per row).
  - Remedy: Refactor to `LEFT JOIN` and `GROUP BY`.

